diff --git a/packages/react-native-web-examples/README.md b/packages/react-native-web-examples/README.md
index 83421cf3..f901547f 100644
--- a/packages/react-native-web-examples/README.md
+++ b/packages/react-native-web-examples/README.md
@@ -1,3 +1,41 @@
 # React Native for Web examples
 
 Next.js pages and React Native components. Provides interactive examples for the documentation website.
+
+## Run locally
+
+From monorepo root:
+
+```bash
+npm run dev -w react-native-web-examples
+```
+
+## Webpack browser mode
+
+This package also supports a simple webpack browser build without changing the current `pages/` structure.
+
+```bash
+npm run dev:webpack -w react-native-web-examples
+```
+
+Production build:
+
+```bash
+npm run build:webpack -w react-native-web-examples
+```
+
+Serving production build:
+
+```bash
+npm run serve:webpack -w react-native-web-examples
+```
+
+Webpack output is generated in `packages/react-native-web-examples/dist-webpack/`.
+
+## Web TV pages
+
+TV-focused examples in this fork:
+* `/tv-event-handler`
+* `/tv-focus-guide-view`
+* `/flatlist-tv-scroll`
+
